<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, black, #1a1a1a, black);
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        div {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: calc(100vh - 81.09px);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        p {
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        div>p {
            max-width: 40rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        footer {
            padding: 1.6rem 1rem;

        }

        footer span {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div>
        <h1>Welcome to Our E-Commerce API</h1>
        <p>This is a modern e-commerce application built with Node.js and Express. Browse our extensive catalog of
            products,
            add items to your cart, create a wishlist, and explore various categories to find exactly what you need.
        </p>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>Created By <span>Elsayed Kewan</span></p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>